headline: 3 Reasons to Sell CHRW and 1 Stock to Buy Instead
summary: What a fantastic six months it’s been for C.H. Robinson Worldwide. Shares of the company have skyrocketed 50.7%, hitting $134.36. This was partly due to its solid quarterly results, and the performance may have investors wondering how to approach the situation.
